  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00089', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設所有財貨的生產皆是固定規模報酬，有關機會成本與國際貿易型態， 下列敘述何者正確？', '["具有絕對利益意味同時擁有比較利益", "假設國家 A 相對於國家 B 在生產電腦時可以用更少的投入得到相同的 產出，則國家A具有生產電腦的比較利益", "假設國家 A 和 B 在生產所有財貨皆有相同的機會成本，則兩國進行國 際貿易不會帶來專業化利得", "假設國家A在生產所有財貨皆較有效率，則兩國進行國際貿易不會互蒙 其利"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00090', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '某財貨的市場需求函數為Q=4-P，其中Q為需求量，P為價格。當價格為 2元時，價格的需求彈性為何？', '["-1/4", "-1", "-2", "-4"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00091', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在兩期模型下，假設第一期的消費與第二期的消費都是正常財。在其他條 件不變下，當利率下跌時，下列敘述何者正確？', '["第一期的消費必定增加", "第一期的消費必定減少", "第二期的消費必定增加", "第二期的消費必定減少"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00092', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '生產函數的斜率定義為下列何者？', '["邊際替代率（marginalrateofsubstitution）", "邊際技術轉換率（marginalrateoftransformation）", "邊際技術替代率（marginalrateoftechnicalsubstitution）", "邊際產量（marginalproduct）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00093', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設廠商的總成本函數為 TC=3Q+10，其中 TC 為總成本，Q 為產量，下 列敘述何者正確？', '["此成本函數為長期成本函數", "平均成本（AC）函數為AC=3", "邊際成本（MC）函數為MC=3", "固定成本（FC）函數為FC=3"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00094', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知一完全競爭廠商，短期總成本函數為TC=q2-8q+110，其中TC為總成本 ，q為產量。若市場的價格為12元，此時廠商最多可賺取的經濟利潤為何？', '["-10", "0", "10", "12"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-7c4986e7-moex-00095', 'disabled-7c4986e7', 'disabled-7c4986e7-moex-113-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-disabled-7c4986e7-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在獨占性競爭市場下，假設廠商有相同的成本，於長期均衡時，下列敘述 何者正確？', '["廠商的平均總成本曲線與邊際成本曲線相交", "廠商的平均總成本曲線與邊際收益曲線相切", "廠商的平均總成本曲線與平均收益曲線相切", "廠商的邊際成本曲線與邊際收益曲線相切"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6f76ab1b056f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "aff3e98fba69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113040", "c": "306", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL)
